==Welcome to the YAPWTP Wiki==

[[YAPTP]] is a pre-alpha WikiText parser currently under heavy development.  It is written in [[Peg/Leg]] and aims to be a lightweight, extremely fast alternative to using [[MediaWiki]] and PHP for parsing WikiText.


It is far from complete.


[[http://yamwtp.drasticcode.com]] is an wiki environment that uses [[YAPWTP]]. Its source code is available on [[http://github.com/samg/wikiwiki|github]].

It goal is to document the current state of [[YAPWTP]] development and demonstrate its current functionality.


You may want to check out:

* [[Parsed Examples]] - Demonstrations of YAPWTP's abilities
* [[Problem Text]] - Examples of where YAPWTP fails to do a good job parsing, and could be improved.